snippet: MORRISSEY--Dolores Josephine, died on March 12, 2016. She is survived by her niece, Meryn Klabouch and many cousins. She was CEO and President of Mutual of America Insurance Company. She was Lady of Charity for the Archdiocese of New York, a board member of Yorkville Pantry, a member of the Malta Society and a member of the Sopromist Organization. Friends may call at Frank E. Campbell-The Funeral Chapel, 1076 Madison Ave., Thursday, 4-8pm. Funeral Mass will be held at St. Joseph's Church, 404 East 87th Street, Friday, 10am. Interment Calvary Cemetery. In lieu of flowers, donations may be made to St. Jean Baptiste High School, 173 - East 75th Street, NY, NY 10021, Attn: Miss Laura Campbell, 212-288-1645. 1/3
